headline: Wells Fargo Upgrades Cintas (CTAS) Stock to Equal Weight, Raises PT
summary: Cintas Corporation (NASDAQ:CTAS) is one of the Top 10 Transportation and Industrial Stocks to Buy Now. Wells Fargo upgraded the company’s stock to “Equal Weight” from “Underweight” with a price objective of $221, up from the prior target of $196, as reported by The Fly. The upgrade demonstrates the firm’s expectation of Cintas Corporation (NASDAQ:CTAS) achieving greater market share gains […]
